The ivory woven jacquard pillow sham creates a unique look in your bedroom with its beautiful paint brush stroke design. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.

transcripts: The brushstroke comforter and bedding collection by Kenneth Cole reaction home was designed exclusively for Bed Bath and Beyond. The first layer of the bed are the euro shams the euro shams add an ideal backdrop to the bed. They are 100 percent cotton in a textured soft creme, the brushstroke comforter and pillow shams are yarn dyed jacquard with a painterly pattern of overlapping brush strokes in ivory and taupe. The coordinating pillow shams are finished with the same brush stroke pattern as the comforter. The resulting bed is soft and calming. The decorative pillows accenting this bed suite are a square mat swirl sequin pillow in rose gold, a rectangular two tone striped pillow in khaki, and in an embroidered Velvet brushstroke pillow in taupe. The pillows add the key fashion elements to complete this bed look. The brushstroke comforter and bedding collection is part of the Kenneth Cole reaction home collection. It is available exclusively online and in select Bed Bath and Beyond stores.
